Package: chirpR
Title: Tools for Analyzing and Handling BirdNET Analyze Results
Version: 0.2.5
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrew J.", "Fairbairn", email = "andrew.fairbairn@tum.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2826-3465"))
Description: A collection of functions for analyzing results produced by BirdNET Analyze.
    These tools support a semi-automated analysis pipeline for ecoacoustic data,
    facilitating tasks like preprocessing, summarizing detections, and calculating vocal activity rates.
